  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink297-kilavi">oruvaḻit taṇantu varaiya vēṇṭum  eṉṟa talaimakaṟkut tōḻi kūṟiyatu</p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> 
          What the confidante told the hero who said that he needed to be temporarily absent and [then] marry.             
        </p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink297">
<l>virinta vēṅkaip peruñciṉait tōkai</l>
<l>pūkkoy makaḷiriṟ ṟōṉṟu nāṭa</l>
<l>piriyiṉum piriva taṉṟē</l>
<l>niṉṉoṭu mēya maṭantai naṭpē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>O man from the land</l>
        <l>where the peacocks on the great branches of the blossoming kino tree</l>
        <l>appear like women who pluck flowers—</l>
        <l>even if [you] separate,</l>
        <l>the intimacy of the girl who is suited to you</l>
        <l>is not one that will separate.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
